v/lib/python3.12/site-packages/jinja2/optimizer.py","title":".venv/lib/python3.12/site-packages/jinja2/optimizer.py","docAuthor":"alcamarga","description":"No description found.","docSource":".venv/lib/python3.12/site-packages/jinja2/optimizer.py","chunkSource":"github://https://github.com/alcamarga/pizzeria-app-core?:efe48fe3eb724052463dc802b4eea417","published":"4/26/2026, 11:03:34 PM","wordCount":372,"token_count_estimate":338,"text":"<document_metadata>\nsourceDocument: .venv/lib/python3.12/site-packages/jinja2/optimizer.py\npublished: 4/26/2026, 11:03:34 PM\n</document_metadata>\n\ndef generic_visit(\n        self, node: nodes.Node, *args: t.Any, **kwargs: t.Any\n    ) -> nodes.Node:\n        node = super().generic_visit(node, *args, **kwargs)\n\n        # Do constant folding. Some other nodes besides Expr have\n        # as_const, but folding them causes errors later on.\n        if isinstance(node, nodes.Expr):\n            try:\n                return nodes.Const.from_untrusted(\n                    node.as_const(args[0] if args else None),\n                    lineno=node.lineno,\n                    environment=self.environment,\n                )\n            except nodes.Impossible:\n                pass\n\n        return node"}}]]